ActInternational Bridges and Tunnels Act
SubjectOrder Approving the Alteration of the Customs Facilities on the Canadian side of the Peace Bridge
PrecisOrder approving the alteration of the customs facilities on the Canadian side of the PEACE BRIDGE in Fort Erie, Ontario in order to build a permanent drive-through structure to facilitate the non-intrusive inspections of commercial vehicles entering the United States in advance of their arrival at a primary inspection booth at the port of entry.
